The [[University of Abertay Dundee]] is a [[New Universities|''new university'']]; created in 1994 under [[Further and Higher Education Act, 1992|legislation]] granting the status of university to the Dundee Institute of Technology, which had been founded in 1888. The university has a [[computer games]] technology and design department that holds an annual computer game production competition called ''Dare to Be Digital''.<ref>{{cite web
