[[Dundee College]] is the city's umbrella [[further education]] college, which was established in 1985 as an institution of higher education and vocational training. The college is noted for its [[New Media]] centre and incorporates the [[Scottish School of Contemporary Dance]]. In a 2005 [[Her Majesty's Inspectorate of Education|HMIE]] inspection, the college's teaching and learning process were rated "very good" in six of the seven subject areas and overall evaluations.<ref>{{cite press release 
